        "subject": "LU-1409 spec: Make spec macros human readable",
        "message": "LU-1409 spec: Make spec macros human readable\n\nI am convinced the proper approach is to wrap unusual tools with\na script akin to the automake \"missing\" script.  It prints a\nhow-to-get-it message when the requested tool is \"missing\".\nThat means this patch degrades to making the spec file macros\nreadable to a normal human being.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruce Korb <bruce_korb@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-488\nChange-Id: If8db4d94d0756c6d9ea364469dde69c90f630ac0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
